{% call components.section("Best practices") -%}

  <h4>Too many links</h4>

  <p>Do not apply lots of links to paragraph text otherwise a user will have trouble reading the content in its entirety before making a selection.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-1.svg" alt="Link component best practice 1" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Multiple link variants</h4>

  <p>Do not use multiple link variants to direct a user to the same destination.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-2.svg" alt="Link component best practice 2" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Ambiguity</h4>

  <p>When writing link text, avoid ambiguous phrases or a full website URL. A user should have a clear idea of where they are being directed to before they make a selection.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-3.svg" alt="Link component best practice 3" style="--inline-img-max-width: 455px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Long links</h4>

  <p>Do not use either link variant with lots of text.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-4.svg" alt="Link component best practice 4" style="--inline-img-max-width: 561px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Buttons</h4>

  <p>Buttons have very different use cases than links and should not be used to promote offers or other content.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-5.svg" alt="Link component best practice 5" style="--inline-img-max-width: 309px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>External link icon</h4>

  <p>Do not apply the external link icon to either Call to action link variant.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-6.svg" alt="Link component best practice 6" style="--inline-img-max-width: 406px;">
  {%- endcall %}

  <h4>Widows</h4>

  <p>The Default call to action variant link arrow and the external link icon should not appear by themselves, they should always be connected to at least one word on the same line.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
    <img src="/assets/link/link-best-practice-7.svg" alt="Link component best practice 7" style="--inline-img-max-width: 360px;">
